2012年5月24日，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]宣布，其已獲得這本書的權利，[[布萊德利·庫柏|布萊德利·庫柏]]將在改編電影中擔任製片及主演<ref name="hollywoodreporter1" />。庫柏曾想過由[[克里斯·普瑞特|克里斯·普瑞特]]飾演凱爾，但華納兄弟同意聘請庫柏擔任主演<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-american-sniper-cooper-hall-20141226-story.html#page=2|title=Makers of 'American Sniper' press ahead to tell a tale of war and home|author=Los Angeles Times|date=2014-12-25|work=latimes.com}}</ref>。9月，[[大衛·歐·羅素|大衛·歐·羅素]]表示有興趣執導該片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/bradley-cooper-david-o-russell-american-sniper/ |title=Bradley Cooper and David O. Russell May Re-team for AMERICAN SNIPER |publisher=Collider.com |date=2013-11-20 |accessdate=2014-04-13}}</ref>。2013年2月2日，{{link-en|克里斯·凱爾與柴德·利特菲爾德謀殺案|Murders of Chris Kyle and Chad Littlefield|克里斯·凱爾遭到謀殺}}。5月2日，宣布[[史蒂芬·史匹柏|史蒂芬·史匹柏]]將擔任導演一職<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/steven-spielbergs-next-movie-american-451011 |title=Steven Spielberg's Next Movie: 'American Sniper' |publisher=Hollywood Reporter |date=2013-02-05 |accessdate=2014-04-13}}</ref>。史匹柏讀過凱爾的書，雖然他希望在劇本中有更多的心理衝突，因此「敵方狙擊手」的角色可視為試圖追蹤並殺死凱爾的叛軍狙擊手。史匹柏的想法促進了長達160頁的劇本的發展。由於華納兄弟的預算限制，史匹柏認為自己無法將他對故事的想法帶到螢幕上<ref name="makingof">{{cite news | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/making-american-sniper-how-an-760963 | title = The Making of 'American Sniper': How an Unlikely Friendship Kickstarted the Clint Eastwood Film | last=Ben Block | first=Alex | publisher = ''[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]]'' | date = 2015-01-02 |quote= a slender $60 million | accessdate = 2015-01-05}}</ref>。8月5日，史匹柏退出導演職位<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming |first=Mike |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/08/steven-spielberg-drops-out-of-directing-american-sniper/ |title=Steven Spielberg Drops Out of Directing 'American Sniper' |publisher=Deadline.com |date= |accessdate=2014-04-13}}</ref>。8月21日，據報導，[[克林·伊斯威特|克林·伊斯威特]]將接手執導<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/clint-eastwood-talks-direct-american-611186 |title=Clint Eastwood in Talks to Direct 'American Sniper' |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2013-08-21 |accessdate=2014-04-13}}</ref>。

=== 選角 ===

2014年3月14日，[[席艾娜·米勒|席艾娜·米勒]]加入演員行列<ref name="slashfilm1" />。3月16日，[[凱爾·蓋納|凱爾·蓋納]]參演電影<ref name="thewrap1" />，而{{link-en|科瑞·哈德里克|Cory Hardrict}}則在3月18日加入<ref name="deadline2" />。3月20日，{{link-en|纳维德·内加班|Navid Negahban}}、[[艾瑞克·克羅斯|艾瑞克·克羅斯]]、[[艾瑞克·拉登|艾瑞克·拉登]]、雷伊·加列戈斯和[[傑克·麥克道曼|傑克·麥克道曼]]加盟劇組<ref name="thewrap2" /><ref name="deadline3" />，3月25日，[[路克·葛萊姆斯|路克·葛萊姆斯]]與[[山姆·賈格|山姆·賈格]]簽署出演電影<ref name="variety1" /><ref name="deadline1" />。前海軍海豹部隊成員{{link-en|凱文·洛茲|Kevin Lacz}}參與演員的行列，並同時擔任一名技術顧問<ref name="fredericksburg1" />。另一名海軍海豹部隊成員喬爾·蘭伯特也以一名[[三角洲部隊|三角洲部隊]]狙擊手的角色加盟電影<ref name="Joel">{{cite news|title=Joel Lambert Books 'American Sniper'|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/brett-dalton-robin-tunney-tessa-thompson-american-sniper/|accessdate=2014-05-17|newspaper=deadline.com|date=2014-05-16}}</ref>。6月3日，[[麥克斯·查爾斯|麥克斯·查爾斯]]參演該片，詮釋凱爾的兒子科爾頓·凱爾<ref name="Charles">{{cite news|last1=Sneider|first1=Jeff|title='Amazing Spider-Man' Actor to Play Bradley Cooper's Son in 'American Sniper'|url=http://www.thewrap.com/young-spider-man-actor-to-play-bradley-coopers-son-in-american-sniper-exclusive/|accessdate=2014-06-09|publisher=thewrap.com|date=2014-06-03}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===

[[主要攝影|主要攝影]]於2014年3月31日在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]開始<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.studiosystemnews.com/on-the-set-for-33114-paul-feig-melissa-mccarthy-start-spy-michael-fassbender-wraps-macbeth/ |title=On The Set For 3/31/14: Paul Feig and Melissa McCarthy Start 'Spy' and Michael Fassbender Wraps 'Macbeth' |publisher=Studiosystemnews.com |date= |accessdate=2014-04-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407074749/http://www.studiosystemnews.com/on-the-set-for-33114-paul-feig-melissa-mccarthy-start-spy-michael-fassbender-wraps-macbeth/ |archivedate=2014-04-07 }}</ref>；劇組也有在[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]拍攝<ref>{{cite news|title='American Sniper', starring Bradley Cooper, filming in Los Angeles this week|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/04/19/american-sniper-starring-bradley-cooper-filming-in-los-angeles-this-week/|accessdate=2014-04-20|newspaper=onlocationvacations.com|date=2014-04-19}}</ref>。4月23日，《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》報導，在阿富汗村莊為期10天的拍攝將於位在[[聖塔克拉利塔|聖塔克拉利塔]]的藍雲電影牧場開始<ref>{{cite news|last=Verrier|first=Richard|title=Eastwood starts shooting 'American Sniper' at Santa Clarita ranch|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/cotown/la-et-ct-on-location-american-sniper-20140423,0,5378053.story#axzz2zlWV6xOW|accessdate=2014-04-26|newspaper=latimes.com|date=2014-04-23}}</ref>。5月7日，電影在[[埃爾森特羅_(加利福尼亞州)|埃爾森特羅]]周圍拍攝時被發現；牛奶工廠用於當作廢棄的[[椰棗|椰棗]]工廠，叛軍在電影的高潮時自四面八方逼近<ref>{{cite news|last1=Rubio|first1=Heric|title=Bradley Cooper and Clint Eastwood set their sights on El Centro for "American Sniper"|url=http://www.ivpressonline.com/open/bradley-cooper-and-clint-eastwood-set-their-sights-on-el/article_0e11c9c0-05f5-525c-ae8c-384233e668c1.html|accessdate=2015-01-18|work=Imperial Valley Press|date=2014-05-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Christine|title=Bradley Cooper filming 'American Sniper' in El Centro, CA this week|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2014/05/08/bradley-cooper-filming-american-sniper-in-el-centro-ca-this-week/|accessdate=2014-05-09|newspaper=onlocationvacations.com|date=2014-05-08}}</ref>。5月14日，庫珀被發現於加利福尼亞州的[[卡爾弗城_(加利福尼亞州)|卡爾弗城]]拍攝一些場景<ref>{{cite news|last=GUSMAROLI|first=DANIELLE|title=Bradley Cooper shows off his bulkier frame on the set of American Sniper with co-star Sienna Miller after gaining a dramatic 40lbs for the role|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2629032/Bradley-Cooper-shows-bulkier-frame-set-American-Sniper-star-Sienna-Miller-gaining-dramatic-40lbs-role.html|accessdate=2014-05-17|newspaper=dailymail.co.uk|date=2014-05-15|location=London}}</ref>，然後他在5月16日於洛杉磯再次進行拍攝作業<ref>{{cite news|title=Bradley Cooper Shoots Scenes for "American Sniper" in LA|url=http://www.gossipcenter.com/american-sniper/bradley-cooper-shoots-scenes-%E2%80%9Camerican-sniper%E2%80%9D-la-1142213|accessdate=2014-05-17|newspaper=gossipcenter.com|date=2014-05-17|archive-date=2014-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140518055131/http://www.gossipcenter.com/american-sniper/bradley-cooper-shoots-scenes-%E2%80%9Camerican-sniper%E2%80%9D-la-1142213|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。5月30日，庫珀和米勒在他們角色的婚禮場景的攝影過程中被發現；他們在{{link-en|瑪瑞娜戴爾瑞|Marina del Rey, California}}的一艘遊艇上拍攝<ref>{{cite news|last=KIRBY|first=IONA|title=You may now kiss the bride! Sienna Miller looks stunning in a wedding dress while smooching Bradley Cooper for American Sniper scene|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2644383/Sienna-Miller-looks-stunning-smooching-Bradley-Cooper-American-Sniper-wedding-scene.html|accessdate=2014-05-31|newspaper=dailymail.co.uk|date=2014-05-31|location=London}}</ref>。碼頭和酒吧的場景於加利福尼亞州的[[海豹灘_(加利福尼亞州)|海豹灘]]拍攝<ref>{{cite news|last1=Boessenkool|first1=Antonie|title=Orange County, please report to the set|work={{link-en|橙縣紀事報|The Orange County Register|Orange County Register}}|date=2015-01-18|page=News 1}}</ref>。

